node.text: Before we wrap up one of the wildest years, we’re taking a look back at our favorite @stockxteam highlights. Through it all, the crew shattered records, launched campaigns, supported important causes, partnered with insanely talented collaborators, AND hit $2.8 billy - all thanks to YOU. 2021, we’re ready for ya 😤

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by StockX on September 20, 2021 tagging @stockxsneakers. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Nike’s innovative Air Zoom Tempo NEXT% silhouette got the Off-White treatment in bold colorways. Each pair dons Virgil Abloh’s signature branding, deconstructed aesthetic, and spiked rubber outsole for a true race shoe look. Tap to shop.
